message.content: cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR. The paper discusses methods for measuring machine intelligence through tasks that involve language and vision, which are common topics in the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper specifically focuses on the task of Visual Question Answering, which is a popular research area in all of these sub-categories. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
